=========================== 07. Jan. 96 ====================================
V1.7

added

-     Closing of the active window with a double-click on the midbutton
      (Template/Tooltype CLOSEWINDOW)

-     Closing of the window where the mousepointer is over
      (Template/Tooltype: ADDLEFTBUTTON)

      Hmm, long time ago. Well, I made some changes before, but I lost those
      sources a few weeks ago (damn).

changed

-     Moved some structures into the BBS-part

=========================== 04. Jun. 95 ====================================
V1.6

added

-     The  last linefeed in the clipboard-buffer (R-Command 'c','v') will be
      deleted  if  using  the  midbutton  for the copying, so the line isn't
      executed immediately and some addings to the line are possible

========================== 07. May. 95 ====================================
V1.5  Not published

changed

-     Replaced DOUBLEMMB with DOUBLEMMBKEY (default RAWMOUSE MIDBUTTON). 
      It's  now  possible  to  define  the  action  for  double-clicking the
      Midbutton.   Because  some programs (like MFR, well I believe it's the
      only one) need the midbutton-event as an ie_Code-event instead of an
      ie_qualifier,  the  tooltype-translation does copy the 3 events (left,
      mid and rightbutton) into the ie_code-field.

-     Some internal changes

=========================== 19. Feb. 95 ====================================
V1.4  Not published

debuged

-     Well, removed 3 bugs. I don't believe it, 3 bugs. ;-)
      1. Had a line which really should not be there. Better tell nobody. ;)
      2. Forgot TAG_DONE for the windows-definitions.
         Caused no problems AFAIK
      3. The windowtitle will now be set correctly. The title wasn't updated
         properly

=========================== 21. Dec. 94 ====================================
V1.3  Not published

added

-     Doubleclick  on  the MidButton created a MidButton-event (IECODE), but
      DirectoryOpus  needs  the  MIDBUTTON-Qualifier  too  for  the  Hotkey.
      Fixed. For  use  with  DOpus, CX_PRIORITY has to be over 100!

===========================  1. Sep. 94 ====================================
V1.2

changed

     - Now the memory and time will only be refreshed when they changed.
       (CPU-Usage down from 2% to 0.2%)

     - Changed the default (icon) for CONWINDOWPATTERN
       to (#?Shell#?|#?Dos#?)

added

     - an application-example


=========================== 13. May  94 ====================================
V1.1 

debuged

     - bug removed which caused ignoring the "WINDOW"-tooltype.

added
    
     - added USEFRONTPUBSCREEN which allows automatic jumping to the
       pubscreen in front

=========================== 12. Feb. 94 ====================================
V1.0 first published version

